{"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"id","preciseIdentifier":"c:*Qo","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"init"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"init"}],"symbolKind":"method","externalID":"c:@M@ScanbotSDK@objc(cs)SBSDKBaseScannerViewFinderConfiguration(im)init","title":"init","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"ScanbotSDK"}]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkbasescannerviewfinderconfiguration\/init"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerViewFinderConfiguration"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerViewFinderConfiguration\/init","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"references":{"doc://net.doo.ScanbotSDK/documentation/ScanbotSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerViewFinderConfiguration/init":{"kind":"symbol","title":"init","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerViewFinderConfiguration\/init","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkbasescannerviewfinderconfiguration\/init","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[]},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotSDK/documentation/ScanbotSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerViewFinderConfiguration":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerViewFinderConfiguration"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerViewFinderConfiguration","role":"symbol","title":"SBSDKBaseScannerViewFinderConfiguration","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerViewFinderConfiguration"}],"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkbasescannerviewfinderconfiguration","abstract":[{"text":"The view finder configuration object for a ‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and its subclasses.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Sometimes it is necessary to limit a live video frame detection or recognition to a certain rectangular area with","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a specific aspect ratio: the region or rectangle of interest. This is where a view finder comes in.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It crops the video frame to that region of interest before passing it to any scanner. Usually","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the performance of scanners gain a benefit from it because less pixels must be processed.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Additionally, to guide the user, the view finder visualizes the region of interest by drawing a rectangle around","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"on the user interface.","type":"text"}]},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotSDK/documentation/ScanbotSDK":{"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotsdk","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Version: 8.0.4","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK","type":"topic","role":"collection","title":"ScanbotSDK"}},"variantOverrides":[{"patch":[{"value":"SBSDKBaseScannerViewFinderConfiguration","op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotSDK~1SBSDKBaseScannerViewFinderConfiguration\/title"},{"value":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerViewFinderConfiguration"}],"op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotS